---+++ !RSV Metrics

Note: A metric is a single test performed by !RSV. A probe is a file that executes one or more metrics. In many cases there is one metric per probe, but not always. Historically, people have talked about &quot;probes&quot;, but metrics are what users should be aware of, so please think and talk about metrics more than you think or talk about probes. :)

